Package: shinyauth
Title: shinyauth adds simple authentication to a shiny app, via a MySQL db
    table of users
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Tim", "Jones", email = "timothy.jones1@amey.co.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package adds authentication, and simple user management tools to a Shinydashboard. It requires a MySQL with a schema in which a users table can be placed.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.3)
